      "text": "Pastoralistis (wandering cattle herders) are finding it increasingly difficult to find pasture for their herds. This is leading to increasing violence between settled farmers, who are growing crops, and pastoralists who bring their cattle onto the land to graze, thus  destroying the crops.  Climate change, population growth and land-grabbing are all contributing to these problems. "
    },
