      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "f042c983bb7a7586",
      "text": "# Topic and how we might work on it with community radio \n\n- Conflict between pastoralists and farmers in Kaduna State and elsewhere \n- Practical work by [[John Dada]] and [[Fantsuam Foundation]] (in Kaduna State) on conflict resolution and peaceful solutions.\n- Collecting background information online at this site:  see [[Farmers and Pastoralists Research Archive]]\n\n- Preparation of radio programme to explore the overlap of interests between the academic community at SOAS and people working practically on farmer-pastoralist issues.\n- Enabling those involved to have a voice through community radio\n- Working with [[Fantsuam Foundation]] to establish a radio studio for the production of podcasts (which will be shared with Internet radio stations elsewhere) and/or will be broadcast via the local fm radio station.  "
